data.description:
Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in the Independence School District! As you walk into the living room, you'll immediately notice the refinished hardwood floors and the abundance of natural light that fills the space. The hardwood floors continue throughout the hallway and bedrooms.

The kitchen and dining area seamlessly flow together, allowing natural light to pour in through numerous windows. Convenience is at your fingertips with the main-level laundry room, offering additional storage space for your everyday needs.

Step out into the spacious fenced yard, where a delightful deck awaits, inviting you to enjoy meals outdoors or simply bask in the fresh air. To cater to your storage or hobby needs, there are two generously sized sheds. One of the sheds is insulated, wired, and equipped with air conditioning.

This is your chance to make this home your own – don't let it slip away!
